Happy International Women’s Day 💗
.
.
Wow it’s been a crazy few weeks, as most of you know my grandpa passed 2/24 and 3 days later my paternal grandmother also passed away. They were both my godparents ❤️ I received these amazing images by @carlyjeanphotography in the midst of all the craziness and I wanted to post them all so bad! I know they would have loved them! Here are a few that I can share on ig 😉 
Life has taught me to live your life how you genuinely want to. Push yourself to be the best version of you. Love yourself, it’s your biggest super power 🥰
